text: Desmiphora niveocincta is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Lane in 1959. It is known from Panama.BioLib.cz - Desmiphora niveocincta. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Desmiphora Category:Beetles described in 1959
